22894, "raw_content": "There are two people in my cat's life, the food goddess, who feeds her, and the shit shoveler, who cleans her litter box.  My cat wants to control when the food comes, so food goddess has to go.  My cat doesn't want to shovel her own shit, so shit shoveler is an ally who must survive the revolution.\n\nSo there are two kinds of leftist: The cats, and the shit shovelers.  The cats talk big about helping the oppressed because they want to replace the oppressors.", "author": "Desensitized", "created": 1783731358587, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "BruddahIz", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "My cat explains leftism.", "last_comment_created": 1783736267150, "content": "<p>There are two people in my cat's life, the food goddess, who feeds her, and the shit shoveler, who cleans her litter box.  My cat wants to control when the food comes, so food goddess has to go.  My cat doesn't want to shovel her own shit, so shit shoveler is an ally who must survive the revolution.</p>\n<p>So there are two kinds of leftist: The cats, and the shit shovelers.  The cats talk big about helping the oppressed because they want to replace the oppressors.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 3, "score_up": 39, "is_edited": true, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2075632748338045253", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ATBqbpPcf", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 53, "suggested_sort